What you need to know:

Former Lazio boss and Italy international Inzaghi, 45, has signed a two-year deal at the San SiroInzaghi, the younger brother of former Juventus and AC Milan striker Filippo, left Lazio last week after a five-year spell in chargeConte led Inter to their 19th Italian league title, and first since Jose Mourinho's treble-winning side in 2010